reSLIRP has been written by Salvador Fandino (sfandino@yahoo.com)
Copyright (c) 2025, All rights reserved.

reSLIRP is just a thin wrapper around libslirp, which is derived from
the original SLIRP code by Danny Gasparovski, so I have decided to
distribute reSLIRP under the same terms. The original license for
libslirp/SLIRP is also included in this software distribution.

